  }, "Ponau\u010Denia na z\xE1ver"), mdx("p", null, "T\xFDch ponau\u010Den\xED by sa dalo n\xE1js\u0165 viac. Spomeniem aspo\u0148 niektor\xE9:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
